# vDSP_desampD

**Function**

Performs double-precision FIR filtering with decimation and antialiasing.

## Declaration

```swift
extern void vDSP_desampD(const double * __A, vDSP_Stride __DF, const double * __F, double * __C, vDSP_Length __N, vDSP_Length __P);
```

## Discussion

This is the same as [doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vDSP_desamp], except for the types of the `A`, `F`, and `C` parameters.

## Real Vectors

- **vDSP_desamp**: Performs single-precision FIR filtering with decimation and antialiasing.
